&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled Solutions Architect to lead the design and optimization of our product’s architecture. In this role, you will serve as the key architect for data solutions, overseeing the integration of advanced technologies while mentoring junior team members and collaborating with cross-functional teams.&lt;/p&gt;
