&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous telesales or junior sales experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal English skills, with strong German language skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence engaging customers via phone and email, including cold calling&lt;/li&gt;
